---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<Base
  title="Holiday Homes Dubai Marina 2026 — From AED 250/night"
  description="Find budget holiday homes in Dubai Marina from AED 250/night. Furnished apartments with marina views. Best area for digital nomads and couples."
>
<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal to-navy text-white py-12 px-4 text-center">
  <div class="text-sm text-green-200 mb-2">📍 Dubai Marina</div>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-3">Holiday Homes Dubai Marina — From AED 250/Night</h1>
  <p class="text-green-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Compare furnished apartments in Dubai Marina. Marina views, walking distance to beach and restaurants. Best value for couples and digital nomads.</p>
  <a href="/get-quotes?ref=marina-homes&type=home" class="bg-yellow-400 text-navy px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-black hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-colors inline-block">Find Marina Holiday Homes →</a>
</div>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy">Holiday Homes in Dubai Marina</h2>
    <p>Dubai Marina offers some of the best-value holiday homes in Dubai's premium areas, with one-bedroom apartments from AED 250/night — slightly cheaper than JBR while still offering beach access via a 10-minute walk or 1 tram stop.</p>
    <p>The Marina has over 200 restaurants, cafes, and bars along the Marina Walk waterfront. It is Dubai's most popular area for digital nomads due to the co-working spaces, fast internet in residential towers, and walkable lifestyle.</p>
    <p>Monthly rates for a furnished one-bedroom in Marina range from AED 5,500–8,000, making it competitive with longer-term hotel stays. Most holiday home operators include cleaning, Wi-Fi, and gym/pool access in the nightly rate.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <a href="/holiday-homes" class="text-teal font-semibold hover:underline">← Back to all holiday home areas</a>
  </div>
</div>
</Base>
